    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> finely</p><p>Trim your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> and chop finely on a diagonal</p><p>Grate your <strong>apple[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and slice into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
