            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Mix the <strong>grated carrot</strong>,<strong> apple</strong>,<strong> sliced sugar snaps</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, and <strong>coriander leaves</strong> with the<strong> sliced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) together in a bowl</p><p>Set aside for later – this is your <strong>sugar snap slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
