        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> dry and add them to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Spread <strong>half</strong> of your<strong> miso paste</strong> (save the rest for later!) over the <strong>basa fillet[s] </strong>and top with the <strong>breadcrumb mixture</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10 min or until the<strong> </strong>breadcrumbs are golden and the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>panko baked basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
