      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>miso paste</strong> with 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir until the sugar has dissolved</p><p>Stir in your <strong>mayo</strong> – this is your<strong> miso mayo</strong></p><p>Add the juice of half of your <strong>lime</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the sugar snap slaw and give everything a good mix up</p>",
