      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are cooked, sprinkle them with the <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> – these are your <strong>sesame chips</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
