      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> panko baked basa</strong> with the <strong>sesame chips</strong>,<strong> sugar snap slaw</strong> and <strong>miso mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
